{"tid":45734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底香港人有幾鐘意炒野","createTime":"2016-12-19T07:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T12:09:09.000Z","uid":2282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb82904a1b4daebe097e7156dd91b014d2acd0cc","tid":45734,"uid":2282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"近排張學友開演唱會 作為孝子的我 就諗住買返兩張孝敬父母啦 點知上網一search 就發現炒到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班炒飛狗 放張飛上網賣 仲好意思話非原價 合理價<br />\n咩叫合理價？合理價佢定架？咁主辦法定個票價出黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家每逢一有演唱會開賣 班炒飛狗就即刻去搶飛 真心想買飛入場支持的人就一張都買唔到<br />\n<br />\n但我估唔到連登都咁多呢d人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/40590/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/40590/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n今日big bang演唱會優先發售 其實我都無咩興趣 但咁岩見到個post就禁入去睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n一禁入去 嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班人係到放飛 好心唔係睇就唔好買啦 見到入面勁多人想買又買唔到 但另一方面就有班人係個post到放飛仲好意思話帶價pm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔知有乜野香港人係唔會炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa5f50054b3d944b9dce2dde9a42ec6e80304f1","tid":45734,"uid":2282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"補返句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果真係唔小心買多左 咪原價放返出黎囉<br />\n可唔可以唔好又要炒 又係到扮唔小心 扮手痕"},{"pid":"1e3e74845035d7fcc8160ea5810c9fb016979185","tid":45734,"uid":58821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"無錢搵既野咪唔會炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d205ef543a7d325985f32272bc9d021aa2fb1584","tid":45734,"uid":18128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"我去排學友諗住同女神睇 我排左成晚 跟住有個阿婆話幫佢個孫買 見佢咁老咪